Good design is durable.

00:30:37.860 --> 00:30:39.193
What does it mean to be durable?

00:30:39.193 --> 00:30:42.500
What does it actually
mean to be durable?

00:30:42.500 --> 00:30:45.839
For the design to be durable.

00:30:45.839 --> 00:30:47.255
AUDIENCE: It's not
going to break.

00:30:47.255 --> 00:30:49.080
It's last.

00:30:49.080 --> 00:30:52.236
PROFESSOR: An object that will
last a decent amount of time.

00:30:52.236 --> 00:30:55.082
AUDIENCE: I mean for the
design to be timeless.

